14.The system shall allow doctors to view the mother’s pregnancy history before labour.
15.The system shall create a labour monitoring record for a patient.
16.The system shall allow doctors to update the current labour or operation stage.
17.The system shall allow nurses to add labour progress notes.
18.The system shall record the condition of the mother during labour.
